{"tid":1558040,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"吳宇森經典執導電影《奪面雙雄 Face Off》將重拍","createTime":"2019-09-10T10:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T08:38:05.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f245b6f63cb022e455667e22a70fd02ebc9d29d7","tid":1558040,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T10:28:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/470/852/4ce.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F470%2F852%2F4ce.gif&h=85ea7264&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nParamount Pictures 於 1997 年推出的動作片《Face Off》（奪面雙雄）由香港大導吳宇森執導，由 John Travolta 與 Nicolas Cage 兩位巨星出演，電影成本耗資 $8,000 萬美金，藉著本片的精彩動作場片獲得不少影迷支持，最終票房達到 $2.45 億美金。<br />\n<br />\n如今，Paramount Pictures 傳將重啟拍攝這部經典動作片，聘請《22 Jump Street》編劇 Oren Uziel 撰寫劇本，《Fast and Furious》系列製作人 Neal Moritz 擔任本片製片，原版製片 David Permut 則轉擔任執行製片。"},{"pid":"b8721cbb8cce31b95b4645dd4f351a67b4b3ea88","tid":1558040,"uid":42848,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T11:08:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PDnW5XxjwI8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPDnW5XxjwI8&d=fwl9YqZIxHA797AeyThx4QDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=807d0def\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PDnW5XxjwI8</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1d088911ad3523e6cf6d9580cf2b490dccb130","tid":1558040,"uid":236422,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"搵邊個拍 都幾難超越到呢兩條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4676a1f9b463b05dd1b93a34b20399fff6ccc3e8","tid":1558040,"uid":214502,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:48:37.000Z","msg":"fuck off"},{"pid":"573b13ecc58758